{"tid":414472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上訪者被當「狗」 慘遭繩圈套頸","createTime":"2017-09-26T09:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T09:09:53.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"125713158538d8770b4053d69b56307852d209ea","tid":414472,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170926/large/1506412265_500a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170926%2Flarge%2F1506412265_500a.jpg&h=e12c54ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有網民在twitter發帖，指山西大同有一上訪民眾在火車被截，其間遭截訪者用繩纏頸，一個繞一個。網民形容這比套狗的「還要好」。有網民指被繩纏頸的是上訪退伍軍人，惟消息無法證實。<br />\n<br />\n而網民形容用繩纏項有如北韓，亦有網友批評這對上訪者是極大恥辱。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\nJasonAyao：這和北朝鮮有什麼兩樣?<br />\n辛勤的搬運工1966：對上訪的人來說是莫大的恥辱<br />\n邪無兮：中國官對中國百姓真好呀，恩情比山高比海深。全世界有良知的人，都來看看吧<br />\n戴鋼盔的豬：可憐的老兵<br />\n末日獨裁&rlm;：可憐可恨他們一個個都不反抗！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170926/57257962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170926%2F57257962&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9fea832d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170926%2F57257962&h=b5fa2743\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170926/57257962</a>"},{"pid":"bb9705f528fd6cba9025b2ae4c69810fc98f4143","tid":414472,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}